modules.description: This module implements a YAML encoder for the `Gendarme` library, specifically handling the conversion of OCaml values into YAML-formatted output. It works with standard OCaml data types such as strings, integers, lists, and records, mapping them to their corresponding YAML representations. Concrete use cases include serializing configuration data, logging structures, and API responses into YAML for external consumption or storage.
